      <title>前新加坡石油大亨林将向清算人支付 35 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/ex-singapore-oil-mogul-lim-set-to-pay-liquidators-3-5-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，林恩奎破产的石油贸易帝国的清算人将从这位破产大亨及其子女手中收回约 35 亿美元，以结束新加坡的民事诉讼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/ex-singapore-oil-mogul-lim-set-to-pay-liquidators-3-5-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 01:54:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市创 2015 年以来最大涨幅，有望进入牛市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/chinese-stocks-head-for-bull-market-as-property-rescue-deepens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股市延续了历史上最引人注目的逆转之一，连续第九天飙升，因为政府的刺激措施吸引投资者重返这个全球受创最严重的市场之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/chinese-stocks-head-for-bull-market-as-property-rescue-deepens</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 01:35:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>野村因违反规定被禁止参与多项日元债券交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/nomura-excluded-from-several-bond-underwritings-on-rule-breach</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于当局发现野村控股公司违反市场规则，该公司被排除在多笔日元债券交易的主承销商之列，这是日本公司今年第二次因违规而取消承销商资格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/nomura-excluded-from-several-bond-underwritings-on-rule-breach</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 00:14:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：中国股市因房地产援助而飙升，日本股市暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-29/japan-stocks-poised-to-fall-on-rate-hike-worries-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国为应对房地产危机所采取的最新举措，周一提振了内地和香港的股市，而东京股市则因日本央行紧缩政策的支持者在执政党领导人竞选中获胜而下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-29/japan-stocks-poised-to-fall-on-rate-hike-worries-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 29 Sep 2024 22:49:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石破天惊的胜利导致日本股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-29/japan-stocks-set-to-fall-on-rate-hike-fears-after-ishiba-s-win-m1o64rpr</link>
      <description><![CDATA[石破茂在执政党总裁选举中意外击败高市早苗，令原本押注其竞争对手将出台更多货币刺激措施带来提振的投资者措手不及，日本股市随之大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-29/japan-stocks-set-to-fall-on-rate-hike-fears-after-ishiba-s-win-m1o64rpr</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 29 Sep 2024 22:44:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
